<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p>Small <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">plaque</rs>/<rs type="objectType">votive relief</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.10</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.08</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.03</measure>) with a relief of <rs type="decoration">two eyes</rs>. Perhaps cut down to left; broken away at right.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face, below the eyes.</p></div><div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>No measurements; square sigma.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
Perhaps <date notBefore="0001" notAfter="0100" exact="none">first century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
